data.description: Back on market! Seller is in process of moving out of state and wants this sold! The first floor offers a large living room with fireplace, separate dining room, kitchen, a wonderful sunroom that opens to the deck, 1st floor laundry and full bath. The second floor has 3 large bedrooms and 2nd full bath. Full unfinished basement offers great storage or finishing potential. A radon mitigation system is installed. Storage shed included. Great home at an affordable price in a super convenient location. Call today for your showing!
